%% Data Flow Diagram - odh-model-controller
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as odh-model-controller<br/>Webhook (9443/TCP TLS)
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Controllers
    participant Istio as Istio Namespace<br/>(istio-system)
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant IGW as istio-ingressgateway<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as KServe Predictor Pod
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User, Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate InferenceService<br/>TLS, API server cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated ISVC
    K8sAPI-->>User: ISVC Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch event received
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route in istio-system<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Gateway server entry<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create cert Secret in istio-system<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig (Authorino)<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshMember<br/>SA token auth

    Note over User, Predictor: Inference Request Flow (Serverless)

    User->>Router: HTTPS/443 TLS Passthrough
    Router->>IGW: HTTPS/8443 TLS
    IGW->>Predictor: HTTP(S) mTLS (mesh)<br/>Auth: Authorino AuthConfig
    Predictor-->>IGW: Prediction Response
    IGW-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User, Predictor: Flow 2: InferenceService (RawDeployment)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route (Edge/Reencrypt)<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create metrics Service + ServiceMonitor<br/>SA token auth

    User->>Router: HTTPS/443 TLS Edge/Reencrypt
    Router->>Predictor: HTTP(S)<br/>Optional auth
    Predictor-->>Router: Prediction Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over Controller, NGC: Flow 3: NIM Account Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Account CR + API key Secret<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Controller->>NGC: Validate API key<br/>HTTPS/443, NGC API key
    NGC-->>Controller: Model data response
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create model data ConfigMap<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServingRuntime Template<br/>SA token auth
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create image pull Secret<br/>SA token auth

    Note over Controller, K8sAPI: Flow 4: Data Connection to Storage Config

    User->>K8sAPI: Create data connection Secret<br/>(opendatahub.io labels)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Aggregate into storage-config Secret<br/>SA token auth
